  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chopped pak choi and cook until wilted, about 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in the lemon juice, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Cook for an additional 2 minutes, stirring frequently.",
    "Stir in the chopped cashew nuts and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Serve the pak choi mixture hot, with lime wedges on the side."
